OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1993FThe first edition of Whatever
OL,7,FHappened To...? airs on BBC One.
OL,8,
OL,9,FRadio Times: "Jan Leeming traces the
OL,10,Fstories that hit the headlines - until
OL,11,Fthe news moved on.
OL,12,
OL,13,F"This week: what happened to the early
OL,14,Fsatellites like Telstar, the children
OL,15,Fwho survived the Aberfan disaster,
OL,16,Fpeace protestors at Greenham Common and
OL,17,FBritain's first Eurovision."
OL,18,
OL,19,FOther presenters on this daytime
OL,20,Fprogramme: Kenneth Kendall, Richard
OL,21,FWhitmore, Gordon Honeycombe and Angela
OL,22,FRippon.
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
