OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2000FHome and Away airs on ITV for
OL,7,Fthe final time, after eleven years on
OL,8,Fthe channel.
OL,9,
OL,10,FThe programme moved to Channel 5, where
OL,11,Fits first airing was on 16th July 2001.
OL,12,
OL,13,FThe gap of just over a year was due to
OL,14,Fa clause in ITV's contract which
OL,15,Fprevented the programme being broadcast
OL,16,Fin the UK for at least twelve months.
OL,17,
OL,18,CG2002FThe first edition of Ant & Dec's
OL,19,FSaturday Night Takeaway airs on ITV 1.
